data.title: Curriculum Vitae Abdulrahman
data.meta_description: Curriculum Vitae Abdulrahman - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This curriculum vitae is for Abdulrahman Mohammed Mohammed Khair Fadhl Allah. He is a Sudanese male born in 1963 who is currently a lecturer in the Department of Radiological Sciences at the College of Applied Medical Sciences, University of Najran in Saudi Arabia. He received a Master's degree in diagnostic ultrasound from the University of Sudan in 2007 and has over 15 years of work experience in radiology and ultrasound technology in Saudi Arabia.
